  "title": "Assistant Accounting Manager[ East/ Full set/ exp managing at least 2 staffs",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to do full set of accounts and generate FS, Sales and Cash Flow reports</li>\n  <li>Have experience in managing at least 2 staffs</li>\n  <li>Manage and reconcile bank transactions</li>\n  <li>Manage Debt collection and AR controller function</li>\n  <li>Process Giro payments to suppliers and vendors</li>\n  <li>File quarterly GST submission</li>\n  <li>Handle tax and audit matters</li>\n  <li>Handle yearly stock take supervision and backend preparation</li>\n  <li>Has Bachelor’s Degree in Accountancy</li>\n  <li>Requires email/Microsoft excel/ Microsoft word knowledge</li>\n  <li>Willing to work in Changi/East area</li>\n  <li>Has experience in using NAVISION software (optional)</li>\n</ul>",
